We lived first in a little

04:26.015 --> 04:55.414
two-room apartment out toward

04:26.015 --> 04:55.414
what we called the Port Arthur Bridge, a very high 
rainbow-shaped structure across the Natchez

04:26.015 --> 04:55.414
River, N-A-C-H-E-S,

04:26.015 --> 04:55.414
until near the end of the spring semester.

